# Build context is V2/. Keep only the node code + constants in the upload.
# NOTE: every pattern here is space-free on purpose. Patterns that referenced the
# "distributed scraper" directory (which contains a space) caused buildkit to
# over-exclude and collapse the whole context, so we don't touch that path here —
# the Dockerfile already copies exactly the node files it needs.

# Heavy DB/seed assets — DB-only, never part of the node image.
src/migrations
src/scraping
src/data

# Caches, bytecode, secrets, runtime logs.
**/__pycache__
**/*.pyc
**/.env
**/logs
